"i" is a song by American rapper Kendrick Lamar, released on September 23, 2014, as the lead single from his upcoming yet-to-be-titled third studio album. The song heavily samples "That Lady", as performed by American R&B group The Isley Brothers, elements of which were re-recorded rather than being directly sampled from the original record. Upon its release, the song debuted in the Top 40 of the US Billboard Hot 100 chart.
